function LuaCSharpAccess:Start()
    --先申请32个数组空间
    local access = AccessCore()
    access:New(32)
    local data = {
        int = access:AInt(2233),
        float = access:AFloat(999.999),
        bool = access:ABool(false),
        double = access:ADouble(22.3333),
        vector3 = access:AVector3(Vector3.New(7, 7, 7)),
        vector4 = access:AVector4(Vector4.New(2, 2, 2.2, 2)),
    }

    self.luaCSharpAccess.cInt = data.int:GetCSharp()
    self.luaCSharpAccess.cFloat = data.float:GetCSharp()
    self.luaCSharpAccess.cBool = data.bool:GetCSharp()
    self.luaCSharpAccess.cDouble = data.double:GetCSharp()
    self.luaCSharpAccess.cVector3 = data.vector3:GetCSharp()
    self.luaCSharpAccess.cVector4 = data.vector4:GetCSharp()
    
    self.luaCSharpAccess.onChangeDataFinish = function()
        Debug.Log("int: {1}", data.int:Get())
        Debug.Log("float: {1}", data.float:Get())
        Debug.Log("bool: {1}", data.bool:Get())
        Debug.Log("double: {1}", data.double:Get())
        Debug.Log("vector3: {1}", data.vector3:Get())
        Debug.Log("vector4: {1}", data.vector4:Get())
    end
    Debug.Log("int: {1}", data.int:Get())
    Debug.Log("float: {1}", data.float:Get())
    Debug.Log("bool: {1}", data.bool:Get())
    Debug.Log("double: {1}", data.double:Get())
    Debug.Log("vector3: {1}", data.vector3:Get())
    Debug.Log("vector4: {1}", data.vector4:Get())
    Debug.Log("Access data set complete, please click change data button!")
end
